t: "la ahd 'ashadu zlmana miman kdhab ealaa allh, fnsb ma hu ealayh min aldalal walbatil 'iilaa allh, 'aw kdhdhab bialhaqi aladhi baeath allah bih rasulih mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wslm, 'iina fi alnaar lmsknana liman kafar ballh, wjhd twhydh wkdhdhab rasulih mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wslm"